#Read Description CSV
Descriptions = pd.read_csv('Patent Descriptions.csv')
#Selecting Important Columns
Descriptions = Descriptions[["Subclass Description (First Four Chars of Subgroup)","Group Description","Group"]]
#Returning First Letter of Class
Descriptions['First'] = Descriptions['Group'].str[0]
#Rename Long Name
Descriptions = Descriptions.rename(columns={Descriptions.columns[0]:"Description"})
#Lowercase everything
Descriptions['Description'] = Descriptions['Description'].str.lower()
Descriptions['Group Description'] = Descriptions['Group Description'].str.lower()
#Searching for certain words
Descriptions['Hardware in Description'] = Descriptions['Description'].str.contains("apparatus|instrument|machine|device|element")
Descriptions['Hardware in Group Description'] = Descriptions['Group Description'].str.contains("apparatus|instrument|machine|device|element")
Descriptions['Software in Description'] = Descriptions['Description'].str.contains("data|computing|software")
Descriptions['Software in Group Description'] = Descriptions['Group Description'].str.contains("data|computing|software")
#Making df a little easier to look at
Descriptions.drop(columns=['Description','Group Description'])
#Final Software/Hardware column
Descriptions['Hardware?'] = Descriptions[['Hardware in Description' or 'Hardware in Group Description']] == True 
Descriptions['Software?'] = Descriptions[['Software in Description' or 'Software in Group Description']] == True 
#Rename 'Group' to 'classid'
Descriptions = Descriptions.rename(columns={'Group':'classid'})
Descriptions
